    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This 2004 Porsche 911 Carrera 4S is a superlative example of the 996.2 generation, featuring the iconic wide-body silhouette and integrated all-wheel-drive system. The 3.6L naturally aspirated flat-six delivers linear power through a precise G96 6-speed manual transaxle. Mechanically, this vehicle is impeccable: the IMS bearing has been proactively addressed with a dual-row ceramic retrofit, and the rear main seal remains perfectly dry. The suspension retains factory-spec geometry with Bilstein dampers providing optimal rebound and compression rates. Braking performance is anchored by four-piston monoblock calipers over cross-drilled rotors, showing zero heat checking or lip. This is a turn-key, investment-grade machine for the discerning purist.",
